# MMSuSiE

MMSuSiE is a Python package for statistical genetics analysis, focusing on sparse genetic relationship matrices and environmental covariates.

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/chaoning/mmsusie.git
cd mmsusie
pip install .
